English:
We need cover when we hack Matayoshi's account.
If Chitose can't come because of work, we won't
have enough people.
Chinese:
在盜取又吉先生的帳號時，得有人拖住他的行動。
千歲因為工作來不了的話……人手會不足。
Korean:
마타요시 씨에게서 계정을 훔쳐낼 때 연극을 벌일 건데
치토세가 일 때문에 오지 못하게 되면……일손이 부족해
German:
Wir brauchen Deckung, wenn wir Matayoshis Account
hacken. Wenn Chitose wegen seiner Arbeit ausfällt,
haben wir nicht genug Leute.

English: Can't you borrow some people from Zaxon?
German: Kannst du dir keine Leute von Zaxon ausleihen?

English:
I don't want to get any other teams involved.
A total outsider would be better...
Chinese:
我不想把其他隊伍的人也牽扯進來，
與其這樣，不如找個完全不相關的人
還比較好……
Korean:
다른 팀은 그다지 끌어들이고 싶지 않아.
차라리 전혀 관계 없는 사람 쪽이 딱 좋은데…
German:
Ich will nicht andere Teams in die Sache
verwickeln. Ein kompletter Außenseiter wäre
besser geeignet ...

English:
Hey, what are you doing now? I got an interesting
book I want to lend you--
Chinese:
嗨，最近在幹麼啊？
我拿到了一本很有趣的書，想把它借給你――
Korean:
여어, 지금 뭐해?
재미있는 책을 입수했으니 빌려주고 싶은데――
German:
He, was machst du gerade? Ich wollte dir ein
interessantes Buch leihen ...

English: Huh? Me? Err, I'm free...but what's up?
Chinese: 嗯？我嗎？有空是有空啦……怎麼啦？
Korean: 응? 나? 한가한데… 무슨 일 있어?
German:
Wer? Ich? Äh, ich hab Zeit ... aber was gibt’s
denn?
